Introduction

Kim Sujung is a South Korean dancer and model under Coreo Entertainment. She is currently a member of the dance crew AXIAL.

Kim Sujung was first known in 2023 for appearing in Street Dance Girl Fighter 2 as a part of the team Mannequeen. She then, from April to June 2024, was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was eliminated in the semi-final (episode 10). During her participation in the show, she was signed with WAKEONE.
